dustrac (1.0.1-1) precise; urgency=low

  * Unlock the first race track.
  * Generate desktop files only on Linux.
  * CMake: Output binaries to CMAKE_BINARY_DIR instead of CMAKE_SOURCE_DIR.
  * Limit the power to 200 kW.

